The paper deals with solving large combinatorial auctions, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of heuristics and optimization techniques also suggests a connection to data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the experimental results and analysis of different algorithms indicate a focus on data mining (cs.DM).
